1:28:01.232 --> 1:28:03.365
looking for people to shoot.

1:28:03.408 --> 1:28:05.192
I hope you get what
you need from this.

1:28:05.236 --> 1:28:06.585
Come on, follow me.

1:28:17.204 --> 1:28:18.597
Tyler, Emma.

1:28:19.685 --> 1:28:20.817
It's Daniel Thomas.

1:28:22.340 --> 1:28:25.256
- You're the gentleman
from the repair shop.

1:28:25.300 --> 1:28:28.390
- This is an odd coincidence.

1:28:28.433 --> 1:28:31.262
Emma, if I'm not mistaken.

1:28:32.437 --> 1:28:34.309
- Yeah, that's it.

1:28:34.352 --> 1:28:35.397
- You guys know each other?

1:28:37.442 --> 1:28:40.445
- Mr. Thomas runs
the repair shop.

1:28:40.489 --> 1:28:42.229
A few days ago
when our car died,

1:28:42.273 --> 1:28:45.407
he helped me get it
towed and repaired.

1:28:45.450 --> 1:28:46.233
- Small world.

1:28:47.670 --> 1:28:51.456
- Mr. Thomas, this
is my husband, Tyler.

1:28:51.500 --> 1:28:53.937
- Mr. Thomas, it's a
pleasure to meet you.

1:28:57.375 --> 1:28:59.464
- That's not what
I came here for.

1:29:04.382 --> 1:29:07.994
- Mr. Thomas, I
would give anything

1:29:08.038 --> 1:29:09.648
to take back what I did.

1:29:09.692 --> 1:29:11.433
There's not a day that goes by

1:29:11.476 --> 1:29:14.479
that I don't regret
what happened.

1:29:14.523 --> 1:29:16.742
It haunts me every
day, and it should.

1:29:20.137 --> 1:29:22.052
Saying sorry won't fix this.

1:29:23.314 --> 1:29:27.187
It won't turn back
time, but sir...

1:29:32.584 --> 1:29:36.022
I'm so sorry for all of it.

1:29:37.372 --> 1:29:38.895
You have to know, I don't
wake up in the morning

1:29:38.938 --> 1:29:41.463
hating anyone,
that's not who I am.

1:29:46.555 --> 1:29:48.383
- Did my son point
a weapon at you?

1:29:52.604 --> 1:29:53.388
- No.

1:29:54.780 --> 1:29:58.393
No, there was no gun
found, he was unarmed.

1:30:04.660 --> 1:30:07.140
- You all expecting
someone else?

1:30:07.184 --> 1:30:08.359
I'll go check it out.

1:30:18.413 --> 1:30:19.762
Can I help you?

1:30:19.805 --> 1:30:21.372
- What the hell
are you doing here?

1:30:21.416 --> 1:30:23.069
- It's a free country, I'm
here visiting a friend.

1:30:23.113 --> 1:30:24.593
- That's exactly
what it better be.

1:30:26.159 --> 1:30:27.857
Where's Tyler?

1:30:27.900 --> 1:30:29.032
- He's over here.

1:30:29.075 --> 1:30:30.425
- You, don't move.

1:30:30.468 --> 1:30:32.252
When I'm done with Tyler,
I'm gonna talk to you.

1:30:37.040 --> 1:30:39.390
- You picked the wrong day.

1:30:39.434 --> 1:30:40.826
- You're under arrest
for aggravated assault

1:30:40.870 --> 1:30:42.175
with a deadly weapon.

1:30:42.219 --> 1:30:43.525
You have the right
to remain silent.

1:30:43.568 --> 1:30:44.874
Anything you say can and
will be used against you

1:30:44.917 --> 1:30:45.657
in a court of law--

1:30:45.701 --> 1:30:46.571
- No, no, no.

1:30:46.615 --> 1:30:47.877
- You the right to an attorney.

1:30:47.920 --> 1:30:48.443
- You don't have
to handcuff him--

1:30:48.486 --> 1:30:50.488
- Son, son, son.

1:30:50.532 --> 1:30:51.533
Calm her down.

1:30:51.576 --> 1:30:52.708
- It's gonna be okay.

1:30:52.751 --> 1:30:54.187
We're gonna get
through this, okay?

1:30:54.231 --> 1:30:55.754
- Take him to the car.
- Let's go.

1:30:55.798 --> 1:30:56.886
- Ma'am, you need to calm down.

1:30:56.929 --> 1:30:58.235
- Wait, wait, wait, wait--

1:30:58.278 --> 1:30:59.628
- You need to calm down
and sit down right--

1:30:59.671 --> 1:31:03.066
- Please, please, please,
please, please, please.

1:32:14.267 --> 1:32:15.617
- All right, everybody.

1:32:15.660 --> 1:32:16.879
Today we have a
very special guest

1:32:16.922 --> 1:32:19.446
for our very first dance class.

1:32:19.490 --> 1:32:22.058
She is one of the best
dancers that I have ever

1:32:22.101 --> 1:32:23.668
had the privilege of watching.

1:32:23.712 --> 1:32:24.930
So what she's gonna do

1:32:24.974 --> 1:32:27.150
is she's gonna perform
a song to dance,

1:32:27.193 --> 1:32:28.717
and then she's gonna
answer questions

1:32:28.760 --> 1:32:31.023
on pretty much how to
become awesome as a dancer.

1:32:31.067 --> 1:32:32.329
Does that sound good?

1:32:32.372 --> 1:32:33.504
-  Yeah!

1:32:33.548 --> 1:32:34.679
- All right, so
let's give it up,

1:32:34.723 --> 1:32:37.334
a very warm welcome to
our very own Miss Kenya!

1:32:40.250 --> 1:32:41.033
- Hey.

1:32:41.077 --> 1:32:42.687
Aw, thank you.

1:32:42.731 --> 1:32:44.602
It's such a privilege to be here

1:32:44.646 --> 1:32:47.518
with such talented
young people today.

1:32:47.562 --> 1:32:49.259
You know, Theo has
told me so many

1:32:49.302 --> 1:32:51.261
great things about you all.

1:32:51.304 --> 1:32:54.438
And today, I will
perform a modern dance

1:32:54.481 --> 1:32:56.571
inspired by love and hope.

1:33:46.533 --> 1:33:47.709
- Hey man, what's up?

1:33:47.752 --> 1:33:49.536
- Have you been checking
the donations account?

1:33:49.580 --> 1:33:51.538
- No, are we overdrawn?

1:33:51.582 --> 1:33:53.889
- You have to take
a look at this.

1:33:53.932 --> 1:33:55.020
- Is this real?

1:33:55.978 --> 1:33:56.805
- Have we been hacked?

1:33:56.848 --> 1:33:58.371
Is this like a joke?

1:33:58.415 --> 1:34:00.373
- No, this is real.

1:34:00.417 --> 1:34:02.549
100%, I've checked.

1:34:02.593 --> 1:34:04.334
In the last week or
so, we've received

1:34:04.377 --> 1:34:06.902
almost a million dollars
in online donations.

1:34:06.945 --> 1:34:08.251
- Oh my goodness.

1:34:08.294 --> 1:34:09.556
- People must've heard
about us on the news.

1:34:09.600 --> 1:34:10.862
-  Oh my gosh.

1:34:10.906 --> 1:34:12.603
- Is this all from one person?

1:34:12.647 --> 1:34:13.517
-  Oh my goodness.

1:34:13.560 --> 1:34:14.692
- No, no, no, look.

1:34:14.736 --> 1:34:17.042
It's small donations,
it's 20 and 50 dollars,

1:34:17.086 --> 1:34:18.870
from people all
over the country.

1:34:18.914 --> 1:34:21.090
There's 20 from
Jason in Little Rock,

1:34:21.133 --> 1:34:23.483
25 from Christie in San Antonio.

1:34:23.527 --> 1:34:24.876
- Oh my good, oh my goodness.

1:34:24.920 --> 1:34:26.791
- There are donations coming
in from other countries.

1:34:26.835 --> 1:34:28.140
- Chris--

1:34:28.184 --> 1:34:29.054
- This is almost twice
as much as we'd of gotten

1:34:29.098 --> 1:34:30.360
if we'd of gotten that grant.

1:34:30.403 --> 1:34:33.798
- Dude, God made a
way, he made a way.

1:34:33.842 --> 1:34:35.670
Oh my goodness.

1:34:43.155 --> 1:34:45.505
I have a confession
to make, little bro.

1:34:48.073 --> 1:34:49.205
I was about to give up.

1:34:51.773 --> 1:34:55.559
I was about to let
mom and dad down,

1:34:55.602 --> 1:34:58.518
let you down, and let
all those kids down.

1:34:59.781 --> 1:35:01.608
And I know this
sounds crazy but,

1:35:03.001 --> 1:35:06.788
I was about to be on that
midnight train to Georgia.

1:35:06.831 --> 1:35:10.661
The idea of you not
making it out of this

1:35:10.705 --> 1:35:11.706
was just too much.

1:35:14.796 --> 1:35:15.884
Then Eric pulled the grant,

1:35:17.755 --> 1:35:20.018
said they had to
protect their brand,

1:35:22.760 --> 1:35:24.719
then I just started
feeling sorry for myself.

1:35:26.721 --> 1:35:28.505
I'm sorry for ever
thinking like that.

1:35:30.550 --> 1:35:32.509
I'm sorry for ever losing faith.

1:35:40.735 --> 1:35:43.563
I had a dream the other
day, a crazy dream.

1:35:43.607 --> 1:35:44.782
I'll tell you about it later.

1:35:46.131 --> 1:35:47.611
I want you to know something.

1:35:50.396 --> 1:35:51.746
That no matter what happens,

1:35:51.789 --> 1:35:53.878
what we started will continue,

1:35:55.619 --> 1:35:57.229
and I'm not gonna give up.

1:35:58.753 --> 1:36:03.148
That we're not gonna give up,
and that your spot is open.

1:36:03.192 --> 1:36:04.846
And that we're gonna
hold it down until

1:36:07.849 --> 1:36:10.547
you're ready to get back
in there, little bro.

1:36:14.464 --> 1:36:15.204
I love you, Drew.

1:36:44.886 --> 1:36:46.496
Today is a dream come true.

1:36:47.889 --> 1:36:51.109
Not only for myself,
but for my family,

1:36:51.153 --> 1:36:53.808
my friends, my colleagues,

1:36:53.851 --> 1:36:54.896
and the amazing group of kids

1:36:54.939 --> 1:36:57.507
we get to work with
on a daily basis.

1:36:57.550 --> 1:36:59.726
We get to do what we love to do,

1:36:59.770 --> 1:37:03.034
while simultaneously giving
back to the community.

1:37:03.078 --> 1:37:04.819
The community we grew up in.

1:37:04.862 --> 1:37:07.865
We feel that it is
within ourselves

1:37:07.909 --> 1:37:09.693
to empower our community,

1:37:09.736 --> 1:37:12.609
and to enable our city.

1:37:12.652 --> 1:37:14.829
This is why the program exists.

1:37:14.872 --> 1:37:17.266
If we can empower
this generation,

1:37:17.309 --> 1:37:20.443
then this generation
can empower the next.

1:37:20.486 --> 1:37:21.923
- For the last six years,

1:37:21.966 --> 1:37:23.750
we've been working
tirelessly to create

1:37:23.794 --> 1:37:25.665
an after school
program that not only

1:37:25.709 --> 1:37:27.493
keeps our kids off the streets,

1:37:27.537 --> 1:37:29.713
but also equips them
with practical tools

1:37:29.756 --> 1:37:31.410
they can use to
enhance their lives

1:37:31.454 --> 1:37:32.977
and the lives of others.

1:37:33.021 --> 1:37:35.458
This program started
with just one class,

1:37:35.501 --> 1:37:37.460
taught by Theo Thomas.

1:37:37.503 --> 1:37:39.070
We still offer that music class

1:37:39.114 --> 1:37:43.596
along with art, dance,
voice, physical education,

1:37:43.640 --> 1:37:46.556
mathematics, English,
and creative writing.

1:37:46.599 --> 1:37:48.993
- And we could not have done
this without all of you.

1:37:49.037 --> 1:37:50.821
Thank you to all the volunteers

1:37:50.865 --> 1:37:53.737
who have been helping
keep us afloat.

1:37:53.780 --> 1:37:56.522
Helping us out whenever
we were short staffed.

1:37:56.566 --> 1:37:58.220
Thanks to the parents
who've been trusting us

1:37:58.263 --> 1:37:59.874
with their kids for
all of these years.

1:37:59.917 --> 1:38:00.962
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

1:38:01.005 --> 1:38:02.833
- And thank you,
thank you to everyone

1:38:02.877 --> 1:38:05.053
who donated to this cause.

1:38:05.096 --> 1:38:08.012
It was overwhelming to
see how many people gave,

1:38:08.056 --> 1:38:10.014
how many people actually
cared about this.

1:38:11.537 --> 1:38:13.583
You know, before I
start to ramble on,

1:38:13.626 --> 1:38:15.759
I want to give the mic
to the guy who said,

1:38:17.065 --> 1:38:19.589
"We should start an
after school program."

1:38:19.632 --> 1:38:23.158
My brother, my
friend, Drew Thomas.

1:38:36.127 --> 1:38:37.999
- Thank you for
the introduction,

1:38:38.042 --> 1:38:40.566
but I don't want to
make this about me.

1:38:40.610 --> 1:38:41.959
This is about these
wonderful kids

1:38:42.003 --> 1:38:45.006
and this great program
that was created for them.

1:38:45.049 --> 1:38:46.833
This is about investing
in the future,

1:38:46.877 --> 1:38:48.923
the future of our community,

1:38:48.966 --> 1:38:51.273
because it has to start with us.

1:38:51.316 --> 1:38:52.970
If we want to see change,

1:38:53.014 --> 1:38:55.842
we have to make those
changes for ourselves.

1:38:55.886 --> 1:38:57.496
And these kids show
up here every day

1:38:57.540 --> 1:38:59.803
because they want to
grow, they want to evolve,

1:38:59.846 --> 1:39:00.935
and they want to change.

1:39:02.719 --> 1:39:04.939
And I'm so grateful I still
get to be a part of that.

1:39:06.723 --> 1:39:09.073
I promised myself I wouldn't
get too emotional but,

1:39:10.683 --> 1:39:13.338
like my brother said,
this is a dream come true.

1:39:15.384 --> 1:39:18.343
So, without further ado--

1:39:19.866 --> 1:39:23.958
- Welcome to the new Clear
Path after school program.

1:39:33.750 --> 1:39:35.186
- Ladies and gentlemen, it's
such a pleasure and honor

1:39:35.230 --> 1:39:36.709
to have you here
at the table today

1:39:36.753 --> 1:39:38.755
to discuss the
situation that happened,

1:39:38.798 --> 1:39:41.627
I really believe the
answers and the solutions

1:39:41.671 --> 1:39:42.933
that we provide today

1:39:42.977 --> 1:39:45.109
are literally gonna have
global implications.

1:39:45.153 --> 1:39:46.502
The problem that we face

1:39:46.545 --> 1:39:48.025
and the thing that
we went through

1:39:48.069 --> 1:39:50.027
is something that is happening
all around the world,

1:39:50.071 --> 1:39:51.768
and we're gonna get
to make a different.

1:39:51.811 --> 1:39:53.204
-  Yes, sir.

1:39:53.248 --> 1:39:54.466
- We're really grateful
that we can use this for--

1:39:54.510 --> 1:39:55.163
- Tyler Garett.

1:39:58.035 --> 1:39:59.080
You wanted to meet me?

1:40:01.038 --> 1:40:02.213
- Yes.

1:40:02.257 --> 1:40:03.171
I wanted to meet you.

1:40:04.781 --> 1:40:07.088
To look you in the eyes,
and tell you how sorry I am

1:40:07.131 --> 1:40:08.785
for what happened.

1:40:08.828 --> 1:40:09.829
I'm sorry for all of it.

1:40:12.310 --> 1:40:13.616
I look at that day and--

1:40:13.659 --> 1:40:17.663
- Tyler, I've forgiven
you, a while ago.

1:40:19.578 --> 1:40:22.625
You know, holding on to
that anger and that hate,

1:40:22.668 --> 1:40:23.974
it was like a poison to me.

1:40:25.019 --> 1:40:26.237
And I had to release it.

1:40:27.543 --> 1:40:30.502
But forgiving you,
it's not enough.

1:40:31.938 --> 1:40:34.071
We need to work together
to figure out solutions

1:40:34.115 --> 1:40:37.509
so this never happens again.

1:40:38.423 --> 1:40:39.250
- I agree.

1:40:40.121 --> 1:40:42.079
Let's figure this thing out.

1:40:42.123 --> 1:40:43.689
- Let's figure it out.

1:41:19.464 --> 1:41:21.162
Now is the time

1:41:21.205 --> 1:41:25.383
to lift our nation from the
quicksands of racial injustice

1:41:25.427 --> 1:41:27.124
to the solid rock
of brotherhood.

1:41:27.168 --> 1:41:28.821
Now is the time!

1:41:32.869 --> 1:41:37.439
There will be neither rest
nor tranquility in America

1:41:37.482 --> 1:41:41.530
until the Negro is granted
his citizenship rights.

1:41:41.573 --> 1:41:44.402
The whirlwinds of revolt
will continue to shake

1:41:44.446 --> 1:41:46.883
the foundations of our nation,

1:41:46.926 --> 1:41:49.973
until the bright days
of justice emerges.

1:41:52.584 --> 1:41:56.022
We must not be guilty
of wrongful deeds.

1:41:57.372 --> 1:42:01.463
Let us not seek to satisfy
our thirst for freedom

1:42:01.506 --> 1:42:05.510
by drinking from the cup
of bitterness and hatred.

1:42:08.122 --> 1:42:11.473
We must forever conduct our
struggle on the high plane

1:42:11.516 --> 1:42:14.084
of dignity and discipline.

1:42:14.128 --> 1:42:18.871
We must not allow our
creative protest to degenerate

1:42:18.915 --> 1:42:21.091
into physical violence.

1:42:21.135 --> 1:42:26.662
Again and again we must
rise to the majestic heights

1:42:26.705 --> 1:42:30.535
of meeting physical
force with soul force.

1:42:30.579 --> 1:42:34.191
The marvelous new militancy
which has engulfed

1:42:34.235 --> 1:42:38.543
the Negro community must
not lead us to a distrust

1:42:38.587 --> 1:42:39.979
of all white people,

1:42:40.023 --> 1:42:42.286
for many of our white brothers,

1:42:42.330 --> 1:42:44.636
as evidenced by their
presence here today,

1:42:44.680 --> 1:42:47.117
have come to realize
that their destiny

1:42:47.161 --> 1:42:49.424
is tied up with our destiny.

1:42:52.688 --> 1:42:54.516
Now is the time.

1:43:16.886 --> 1:43:18.061
Now is the time.

